 4. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 5. the fan of metal is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 6. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
 7. the designer is on the left of the fisherman##1
 8. the fan of house is on the far right##1
 9. the accountant is between the social-worker and the person who's sport is cycling##2
10. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growsiris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Flower          | amaryllis        | iris    | balloon-flower | rose   |
